values:
So I'm moving. I feel like consolidating my usernames. Therefore, this journal will remain open, but most entries are no longer around. My new journal is coconut_sara.  

Friend me.

Or else.

If you want me to friend you, let me know, as all my entries will be friends only.  Why?  Because scary things can happen with blogs.  Less scary things happen if entries are only accessible to few.  

So yeah.
